---
title: Hot Open-Faced Turkey Sandwich with Sage Gravy Sweet Potato Mash and Green Peas
description: Sliced roast turkey piled high on garlic toast and slathered in hot sage gravy...YUMMY! Creamy sweet potato mash and green beans round out this comforting family dinner.
